These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
City: hannover, rome, new-york, boston
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person eating mango is the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| City   | rome  | hannover     | new-york   | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
City: hannover, rome, nizza, berlin
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| City   | nizza    | rome      | hannover | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, turtle, cat
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Pet   | hamster   | turtle | cat | lizard         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, purple, lilac, blood-red
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | blood-red | purple | turquise  | lilac      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, azure, amber, mauve
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Color    | chestnut       | mauve | amber | azure     |

