.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, drama, superhero, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero | epic      | drama | horror |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

