There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, russian, japanese, australian
1. the australian is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the russian is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the australian is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy       | family | zombie   |
| Nationality     | russian | japanese | australian   | turkish |

