.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, mechanic, freelancer, dancer
1. the security-guard is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Job   | dancer | freelancer | mechanic          | security-guard    |

