.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
City: liverpool, rome, berlin, prague
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, disco, r&b
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of disco##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to rome is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| City      | berlin | rome  | liverpool | prague |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | disco | r&b           | d&b   |

