3. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
4. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
5. the person eating apple is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | thai | dutch  |
| Food           | pineapple | radish      | apple | lettuce |

