.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, swimming, soccer, climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, scientific, spy
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | swimming | soccer | climbing | rugby |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | scientific    | action      | drama   |

