.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil, bellflower, daisy
1. the person who growsiris is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the nigerian is the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Flower     | bellflower  | iris    | daffodil       | daisy |

 